name: Cyclone 1
Lore: 'Enclosed armored transport adapted for hot climates by replacing tertiary weapons systems with additional Sienar t23 heat dissipation units.',
Text: 'Power +1 for each Sandtrooper present. Permanent pilots provide total ability of 2. May add 7 passengers. Once per game, may deploy a vehicle site or vehicle weapon aboard from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4.',
